nodes.text: When Jedi Master Obi-Wan Kenobi arrived to Mandalore, this Mandalorian guard said that Duchess Satine Kryze was waiting for him. He then brought Kenobi to the Palace where he would meet with the Duchess.
The Mandalorian Guard was voiced by Matt Lanter, who also voiced Anakin Skywalker in The Clone Wars TV series.
